<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>90</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. A lalna kum sawtin lun zing intin,
 A hauhsakna hai ta puona;
 Khawvel hawihna leh lopina,
 Cheng chu hung bei ina.

[V2]
 Zie khawvel hi mang mah lele,
 Lalpa'n kei din mun ei guotsak;
 Len-guol deih leh Angel vamte cheng tawh,
 Khawvel ngai loa lenna ding.

[V3]
 2. Zie khawvel khel kumsawt mun nuom achun,
 Thiemgau, martar, Angel vam tawh;
 A phaiphuleng uh gi hawih tawh,
 A Lalpau min pakcha'n.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa leh Angel vamte lenna,
 Ka ngai na e khen lohna gam;
 Khawvel ahin lungkham, dahum,
 Kahna i tuokkit sek.

[V5]
 4. Zailan chawian hitiu i Lalpau chu,
 Khawvel cheng hi bei mah lele;
 Kumsawt chanin chawihatna la'n,
 Daihni nei ta pouna.</lyrics>
<title>A Lalna Gam!</title>
</song>